The evidence with the title '5 ridiculous gun myths everyone believes (thanks to movies ... ' says Jun 15, 2010  ... Itty-bitty handguns aren't the only things you can silence.  ... An unsilenced gunshot is around 140 to 160 decibels--that's in the range  ... So a silencer really just makes a large gun sound like a smaller gun.  ... Gun, Hollywood takes this as a blank check to treat the inside of a gun as a magical bullet factory. 
